    }

    /* RESOURCES */
    .resources-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; }
    .resource-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      padding-bottom: 12px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #F3F4F6;
    }
    .resource-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; padding-bottom: 0; }
    .resource-icon {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      background-color: #F5F3FF;
      border-radius: 6px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #7C3AED;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .resource-text { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
    .resource-label {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #0F1535;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .resource-sub {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6B7280;
      margin: 2px 0 0 0;
    }
    .resource-link {
      color: #7C3AED;
      text-decoration: none;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .resource-link:hover { color: #5B21B6; }

    .meta-box {
      background-color: white;
      border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px 22px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .meta-icon {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      background-color: #F5F3FF;
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #7C3AED;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .meta-label {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #0F1535;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .meta-value {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #4B5563;
      margin: 4px 0 0 0;
    }
  </style>

  <div class="meth-page">
    <h1 class="meth-title">Methodology &amp; Data</h1>
    <p class="meth-intro">
      This project uses a panel regression approach to examine how state
      characteristics are associated with NIH research funding per Alzheimer's
      death over the period 2019–2023.
    </p>

    <div class="meth-grid">
      <div class="meth-main">

        <!-- OUR APPROACH -->
        <div class="panel">
          <h2 class="panel-title">Our Approach</h2>
          <div class="approach-grid">
            <div class="approach-step">
              <div class="approach-icon-wrap">
                <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"/><path d="M3 5v14a9 3 0 0 0 18 0V5"/><path d="M3 12a9 3 0 0 0 18 0"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div class="approach-num">1</div>
              <h4 class="approach-step-title">Data Collection</h4>
              <p class="approach-step-body">
                Gathered data from federal sources on AD mortality, NIH funding,
                and state demographics.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="approach-step">
              <div class="approach-icon-wrap">
                <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="22 3 2 3 10 12.46 10 19 14 21 14 12.46 22 3"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div class="approach-num">2</div>
              <h4 class="approach-step-title">Data Processing</h4>
              <p class="approach-step-body">
                Cleaned, merged, and standardized datasets across all states
                and years (2019–2023).
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="approach-step">
              <div class="approach-icon-wrap">
                <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div class="approach-num">3</div>
              <h4 class="approach-step-title">Econometric Analysis</h4>
              <p class="approach-step-body">
                Pooled OLS with HC3 robust standard errors to identify factors
                associated with funding per death.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="approach-step">
              <div class="approach-icon-wrap">
                <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><line x1="9" y1="3" x2="9" y2="21"/><line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div class="approach-num">4</div>
              <h4 class="approach-step-title">Derive Metrics</h4>
              <p class="approach-step-body">
                Computed funding per death and per 65+ resident, plus regional
                aggregates and rankings.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="approach-step">
              <div class="approach-icon-wrap">
                <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/><path d="M12 2a8 8 0 0 0-8 8c0 6 8 12 8 12s8-6 8-12a8 8 0 0 0-8-8z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div class="approach-num">5</div>
              <h4 class="approach-step-title">Visualization</h4>
              <p class="approach-step-body">
                Built interactive tools to explore patterns, disparities, and
                trends across states.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- REGRESSION RESULTS -->
        <div class="panel">
          <h2 class="panel-title">Regression Results: Factors Associated with NIH Funding</h2>
          <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #6B7280; margin: -12px 0 18px 0;">
            Dependent variable: Total NIH AD research funding per state-year (USD)
          </p>

          <table class="reg-table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Variable</th>
                <th>Description</th>
                <th class="num">Coefficient</th>
                <th class="num">Std. Error</th>
                <th class="num">p-value</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              {reg.coefficients.filter(c => c.raw_name !== "const").map((c) => (
                <tr>
                  <td class="reg-var">{c.variable}</td>
                  <td class="reg-desc">{c.description}</td>
                  <td class="num">{formatCoef(c.coefficient)}</td>
                  <td class="num">{formatCoef(c.std_error)}</td>
                  <td class="num">{pValueDisplay(c.p_value)} {pValueStars(c.p_value)}</td>
                </tr>
              ))}
              {reg.coefficients.filter(c => c.raw_name === "const").map((c) => (
                <tr>
                  <td class="reg-var">Constant</td>
                  <td class="reg-desc">Intercept</td>
                  <td class="num">{formatCoef(c.coefficient)}</td>
                  <td class="num">{formatCoef(c.std_error)}</td>
                  <td class="num">{pValueDisplay(c.p_value)} {pValueStars(c.p_value)}</td>
                </tr>
              ))}
            </tbody>
          </table>

          <div class="reg-summary">
            <div class="reg-summary-icon">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="reg-summary-text">
              <div class="reg-summary-stats">
                <span>R² = {reg.r_squared}</span>
                <span>Adj. R² = {reg.adj_r_squared}</span>
                <span>F = {reg.f_statistic}</span>
                <span>p &lt; 0.001</span>
                <span>N = {reg.n_observations}</span>
              </div>
              <div style="margin-top: 6px;">
                Research infrastructure (R1 universities) is the strongest predictor of funding per death,
                not disease burden. Mortality rate is not statistically significant.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #9CA3AF; margin: 14px 0 0 0;">
            Significance: *** p &lt; 0.001, ** p &lt; 0.01, * p &lt; 0.05
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- IMPORTANT NOTE -->
        <div class="callout callout-warn">
          <div class="callout-icon">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="callout-title">Important Note</p>
            <p class="callout-body">
              This analysis is observational and cannot prove causation.
              Funding decisions are influenced by many factors not captured in
              this model, including research quality, historical investments,
              and strategic priorities. The regression results reflect the
              final cleaned dataset; the published paper reports preliminary
              values for some coefficients from an earlier version of the
              analysis. Qualitative findings — particularly that mortality
              rate is not a statistically significant predictor of NIH funding —
              are identical across both versions.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- COMMITMENT TO TRANSPARENCY -->
        <div class="callout callout-trans">
          <div class="callout-icon">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="callout-title">Commitment to Transparency</p>
            <p class="callout-body">
              All data, code, and methodology are publicly available to ensure
              transparency, reproducibility, and continued research into
              health equity and research funding.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- SIDEBAR -->
      <div class="meth-side">
        <div class="panel">
          <h2 class="panel-title">Data Sources</h2>
          <div class="sources-list">
            <div class="source-row">
              <div class="source-icon">CDC</div>
              <div>
                <p class="source-name">CDC WONDER (2019–2023)</p>
                <p class="source-desc">Alzheimer's disease mortality (ICD-10 G30)</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="source-row">
              <div class="source-icon">NIH</div>
              <div>
                <p class="source-name">NIH RePORTER (2019–2023)</p>
                <p class="source-desc">NIH research project funding tagged "Alzheimer's Disease"</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="source-row">
              <div class="source-icon">★</div>
              <div>
                <p class="source-name">NORC Dementia DataHub</p>
                <p class="source-desc">State-level dementia prevalence estimates</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="source-row">
              <div class="source-icon">CB</div>
              <div>
                <p class="source-name">U.S. Census Bureau (2019–2023)</p>
                <p class="source-desc">State population estimates and demographics</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="source-row">
              <div class="source-icon">BLS</div>
              <div>
                <p class="source-name">Bureau of Labor Statistics</p>
                <p class="source-desc">Consumer Price Index for inflation adjustment to 2024 USD</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel">
          <h2 class="panel-title">Project Resources</h2>
          <div class="resources-list">
            <div class="resource-row">
              <div class="resource-icon">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div class="resource-text">
                <p class="resource-label">Research Paper (PDF)</p>
                <p class="resource-sub">Full paper with methodology and results</p>
              </div>
              <a href="/paper.pdf" class="resource-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Open paper">
                <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/></svg>
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="resource-row">
              <div class="resource-icon">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M12 .297c-6.63 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.303 3.438 9.8 8.205 11.385.6.113.82-.258.82-.577 0-.285-.01-1.04-.015-2.04-3.338.724-4.042-1.61-4.042-1.61C4.422 18.07 3.633 17.7 3.633 17.7c-1.087-.744.084-.729.084-.729 1.205.084 1.838 1.236 1.838 1.236 1.07 1.835 2.809 1.305 3.495.998.108-.776.417-1.305.76-1.605-2.665-.3-5.466-1.332-5.466-5.93 0-1.31.465-2.38 1.235-3.22-.135-.303-.54-1.523.105-3.176 0 0 1.005-.322 3.3 1.23.96-.267 1.98-.4 3-.405 1.02.005 2.04.138 3 .405 2.28-1.552 3.285-1.23 3.285-1.23.645 1.653.24 2.873.12 3.176.765.84 1.23 1.91 1.23 3.22 0 4.61-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.92.42.36.81 1.096.81 2.22 0 1.606-.015 2.896-.015 3.286 0 .315.21.69.825.57C20.565 22.092 24 17.592 24 12.297c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div class="resource-text">
                <p class="resource-label">GitHub Repository</p>
                <p class="resource-sub">Code, data, and documentation</p>
              </div>
              <a href="https://github.com/neha-k-reddy/alzheimers-funding-alignment" class="resource-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Open GitHub repo">
                <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/></svg>
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="resource-row">
              <div class="resource-icon">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"/><path d="M3 5v14a9 3 0 0 0 18 0V5"/><path d="M3 12a9 3 0 0 0 18 0"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div class="resource-text">
                <p class="resource-label">Final Dataset</p>
                <p class="resource-sub">51 states × 5 years panel (CSV)</p>
              </div>
              <a href="https://github.com/neha-k-reddy/alzheimers-funding-alignment/blob/main/data/final_dataset.csv" class="resource-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Open dataset">
                <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/></svg>
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="resource-row">
              <div class="resource-icon">
